info: The impact of the project will be increased energy security. The outcome will be that customers within the project area have access to a higher share of electricity generated by hydropower. The outputs are expected to be (i) EPC implements 2.5 MW of hydropower capacity in the project area; (ii) Operation and maintenance knowledge transfer program, and (iii) Efficient project management services.
name: RENEWABLE ENERGY DEV'L & POWER SECTOR REHABILITATI
